import React from "react";

function Regist() {

    

    return (
        <>
            <FormAuth action="POST">
                <Input
                    placeholder="Введите логин"
                    size="md"
                    variant="soft"
                />
                <Input
                    placeholder="Введите пароль"
                    size="md"
                    variant="soft"
                />
                <Button type="submit" onClick={function(){}}>Войти</Button>
            </FormAuth>
        </>
    )
}

export default Regist
